name: Shanti Lodge
address: Bengkel Sari, Selemadeg Barat, Tabanan Regency, Bali 82162, Indonesia
review 1: Shanti Lodge is the best place to spend the holidays. We have been bringing guests, groups, our family and even ourselves to spend a few days or sometimes an entire week at the Lodge. 3 main points on why this place is perfect : 1) The landscape and architecture is peaceful and well decorated, 2) the staff is super helpful in every aspects and even if they are always at the lodge, they let your privacy be, 3) The meals and snacks are healthy and delicious. We recommend the lodge more than any other places on the planet. Thanks for this peaceful retreat/lodge!!!
review 2:
